      ["sys","RELAY","01:47. He arrived in a town car. Jacket, no tie, pocket square folded to look accidental. Brought his own water — the branded kind with his logo. He's already shaken the hand of every person in the building and asked what they do for a living. The microphone he treats like an old friend."],
      ["guest","Sterling Crane","Great to be here. Love the underground thing — very authentic, very counter-culture, my audience is going to eat this up. Housekeeping before we start: the book is 'They Buried The Calendar,' available everywhere, audiobook's narrated by ME, there's a weekend workshop in Austin next month, but we'll get to all that organically. Don't want to be THAT guy. [he is absolutely that guy] Let's do this."]
