       fx:{hype:17,heat:5,rapport:-6},
       reply:["guest","Sterling Crane","[a half-second of genuine surprise, then a grin] ...Caught on the FIRST pitch. [laughs] Fair. FAIR. Most hosts let me get through two plugs and a promo code before they push. You caught it at the door. [adjusts in his chair] Okay. Cards down. No plugs till I've said something that scares me. Deal? And I DO have something that scares me, which is why I picked a pirate frequency at 2 A.M. instead of a podcast with sponsors. You want the version without the wrapper. I respect that. Let's unwrap."],
